{"tid":354300,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(求屌醒) 做野好辛苦 好想試下食煙","createTime":"2017-08-10T10:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T12:49:49.000Z","uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"387d3f026d7c0649bc8147815e5b3206f69a2540","tid":354300,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:21:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 <br />\n做野真係好辛苦 好大壓力<br />\n好想試下食支煙減壓<br />\n<br />\n由細到大都好堅持一定唔食煙<br />\n但開始有d動搖<br />\n日日營營役役 <br />\n都唔知為咩 <br />\n屌 <br />\n<br />\n開始覺得自己個靈魂可以消失一樣<br />\n對所有野變得麻木<br />\n但又離唔開呢份工住 <br />\n因為未完約 仲有5個月<br />\n<br />\n求大家屌醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌到我唔好食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6739520d6217a0873762b9575b6ac91411ddc9a3","tid":354300,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:22:38.000Z","msg":"試下食煙仔餅"},{"pid":"b39a8b0c0d4faacc2f0f7939142427422d1554d8","tid":354300,"uid":133674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:23:06.000Z","msg":"非gay 唔屌男人 sor 下位唔該"},{"pid":"0d82922909af2f408e2ae32c2383bd84426cd060","tid":354300,"uid":19542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:25:04.000Z","msg":"唔好食 食完都唔會減到壓<br />\n<br />\n利申:煙鏟"},{"pid":"d2f37a3c579d2d938e20d1f47cebb5eca213f061","tid":354300,"uid":72979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:35:13.000Z","msg":"其實你有呢個諗法<br />\n我諗你已經諗左一排<br />\n食煙唔一定減壓 睇下你身邊人抗唔抗拒<br />\n絕對唔建議你去食 又哂錢又傷身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但食還食 自己控制番個煙癮<br />\n<br />\n利申:煙鏟"},{"pid":"9102e7deee14cec1307cfc881eb0d32266b1f22c","tid":354300,"uid":108497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:39:20.000Z","msg":"做野辛苦一時 食煙危害一生"},{"pid":"a5fdf95b444860af032face9b69d7f9650e825c3","tid":354300,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:44:09.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪<br />\n有壓力就要食煙？<br />\n做運動 睇下書 打飛機 叫雞都減到壓啦<br />\n傻閪"},{"pid":"258cb8b5ba1a66a6dd8ec97c760f7d144b77d686","tid":354300,"uid":46609,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:44:11.000Z","msg":"想就做啦，唔好掂黃賭毒就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁大個人，有d野唔試唔心熄，你依家唔食，遲下又會諗想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09653f1df116cecc3d0212444afa7572ee7d92e0","tid":354300,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:48:49.000Z","msg":"前排都有你呢個心態"},{"pid":"92833be07b53e89e81299b329695e93b4842821d","tid":354300,"uid":102110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:51:52.000Z","msg":"食完都減唔到，又傷肺，食黎做乜"},{"pid":"14abe8401438c932c652938aeeef41f0dacff0f6","tid":354300,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"火車頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b14cef426446416c7e6621ddab84736114db13","tid":354300,"uid":60193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:53:01.000Z","msg":"唔會減壓，反而一度食會一度諗啲野點做。<br />\n但往往啲解決辦法都係食緊煙果陣諗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7a6850ed57450479fbe232e3a4922bf97e5c9d","tid":354300,"uid":4955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:54:44.000Z","msg":"想食咪試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4905c7c56986a45aa9f459d7a17c327f13af52","tid":354300,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:55:14.000Z","msg":"點解會有食完煙可以減壓呢個咁on9既念頭"},{"pid":"acba33aa37512c9aa9bb7e1fe57706b60539e78b","tid":354300,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:57:44.000Z","msg":"減唔減壓睇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但食完條腸會好辛苦 唔知點解<br />\n<br />\n之後會痾屎"},{"pid":"e6fbafdc12e45da1024757a212e7e2b4063b5c91","tid":354300,"uid":117572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T12:47:45.000Z","msg":"好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日如是既生活真係。"},{"pid":"93c514ad4cc35ffa2a6930a143f19e70de871a05","tid":354300,"uid":39683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"食煙其實好無謂，隊草實際好多，又減壓，又會high, 胃口都好啲"}]}